{"tid":1187072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆竊事敗反遭女屋主五花大綁強姦 男賊報警求助網民：電視劇都不敢這麼演","createTime":"2019-06-05T11:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T11:50:25.000Z","uid":1735,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a7e307213492abded0043faf2523b54bf2757e45","tid":1187072,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"河南省鄭州一名女子深夜返家突然有小偷，靈機一動拿繩子綁住小偷，單身已久的她覺得該男長得不錯，就藉著酒意強行和他發生關係；男子覺得受到奇恥大辱報警。網友事後紛紛為男子鳴不平，「估計這女的是女版張飛。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C9wa52D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC9wa52D.png&h=7755c597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地媒體報導，40歲的韓女3日深夜和朋友喝酒慶生回到家中，發現一名30歲左右的男子正在她家裡翻箱倒櫃，門市裡的收款機和保險箱全部被撬開。韓女見狀後立即拿繩子從背後將其捆住，身材瘦弱的小偷不是她的對手，被她五花大綁制伏了。<br />\n<br />\n據報，韓女制伏小偷後沒有馬上報警，而是將他綁在家中，她看著這名男子長相還可以，加上喝了點酒，竟強行與男子發生了關係。隨後將其鬆綁放走了這名男子。事後男子感覺自己受到了奇恥大辱，認為自己才是受害者，離開後選擇報警。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sn2Bg9n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsn2Bg9n.png&h=48c62f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後韓女被警方批評教育了一番，而男子則以入室盜竊的罪名被拘留。網友爆笑稱，「電視劇都不敢這麼演」、「男小偷都不是對手，很快就被制伏了，估計這女的是女版張飛。」、「偷的最屈辱的一次」、「真是單身久了看誰都眉清目秀」。不過也有網友為小偷打抱不平，認為明明就是性侵，「這女的性侵都不用判刑麽？這是在歧視男性麽」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z50nW9u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz50nW9u.png&h=214c7452&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9002272d5a64030f6ae1763f501b109cce4c9a9","tid":1187072,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:19:55.000Z","msg":"Source<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.popnews.hk/?p=42907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2F%3Fp%3D42907&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=1d7f47e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.popnews.hk/?p=42907</a>"},{"pid":"55fd79cc3bbb304ecbf3e6c7f3d42c6ab12e3897","tid":1187072,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc70854beb84f16e6a9e41d1df98c72d5ed0af7","tid":1187072,"uid":49336,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗強姦嚴重過爆竊 不過女人真係大曬"},{"pid":"2e6146ae623d8c1e74a5c2f038d5279c2b51ef6d","tid":1187072,"uid":1735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"快點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a0ab8903ed13e24d50dc1522c0641fb4bfd299","tid":1187072,"uid":104138,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:24:14.000Z","msg":"韓女見狀後立即拿繩子從背後將其捆住，身材瘦弱的小偷不是她的對手，被她五花大綁制伏了。<br />\n<br />\n 一定係肥婆"},{"pid":"442a3a8eca15820759b085bab920628b338e2902","tid":1187072,"uid":62710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:25:24.000Z","msg":"問題核心係<br />\n如果你唔想 條j會唔會硬"},{"pid":"c855f4dbff204a050f431b66737c8ab6449e81d6","tid":1187072,"uid":48521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"442a3a8eca15820759b085bab920628b338e2902","tid":1187072,"uid":62710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:25:24.000Z","msg":"問題核心係<br />\n如果你唔想 條j會唔會硬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:31:56.000Z","msg":"咁係唔係濕佐唔計強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba58d385e4206e0025cea8a2da07f9137020f288","tid":1187072,"uid":34854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />check清楚屋主咩樣咩人先爆啦"},{"pid":"e756f6534e1d5bb17bee03829092f26f0baeea70","tid":1187072,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5a0ab8903ed13e24d50dc1522c0641fb4bfd299","tid":1187072,"uid":10413